Interface IsaacViewI

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    ConceptCreationViewI, ConceptViewI, ContentRequestHandlerI, DockedViewI, EmbeddableViewI, InfoModelViewI, IsaacViewWithMenusI, ListBatchViewI, PopupConceptViewI, PopupViewI, RefexCreationViewI, RefexViewI, RefsetSearchViewI, TaxonomyViewI, WorkflowAdvancementViewI, WorkflowHistoryViewI, WorkflowInitiationViewI, WorkflowTaskDetailsViewI, XMLViewI
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AboutView, AddRefexPopup, AddUserDialog, ChangePasswordDialog, ClassifierDialogView, CommentDialogView, ConceptCreationWizard, ConceptModelingPopup, ConceptView, ConfigureDynamicRefexIndexingView, CreateMappingItemView, CreateMappingSetView, CreateMetadataView, DescriptionModelingPopup, DynamicReferencedItemsView, DynamicRefexListView, DynamicRefexView, EditMappingItemView, EnhancedConceptView, EnhancedSearchView, ExportFileSettingsDialogView, ImportedModelsView, ImportSettingsDialogView, IndexView, InfoModelView, LegoListView, ListBatchView, LoincContentRequestHandler, Mapping, ModelingPopup, PreferencesView, RefexCreationWizard, RelationshipModelingPopup, SctTreeViewDockedView, SctTreeViewIsaacView, SearchView, SyncView, UscrsContentRequestHandler, WorkflowAdvancementView, WorkflowHistoryView, WorkflowInbox, WorkflowInitiationView, WorkflowTaskDetailsView, XMLDisplayWindow

    @Contract
public interface IsaacViewI
    IsaacViewI The lowest level of a Viewable Isaac component - doesn't actually provide any specific hooks. All components should implement a sub-interface of this.
